      <Term type="command">initialize</Term> - Initialize the server
    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <Term type="command">initialize</Term> command performs a one-time server initialization. Specifically,
      the command creates all necessary tables in the configured database server, and creates an initial administrator
      user with the provided parameters.
